Chris: Chris wants to send flowers to Robin so he contacts Fred his florist.
Chris gives Fred Robin's address, how much to spend and type of flowers to send Robin

Fred's Responsibilities: to contact a florist in Robin's city giving him all the information
he received from Chris.

Robbin's Florist's Responsibilities: The florist orders from the Wholesaler the requested flowers,
contacts the flower arranger to arrange the flowers nicely for Robin
After everything is taken care of the florist then contacts the delivery person to deliver the
marvelous flowers to Robin

Wholesaler's Responsibilities: The wholesaler checks for the flowers' availability and
contacts the flower grower in case any flowers are missing from Robin's florist's order.
After he receives all the required flowers from the grower he then supplies all of the flowers to
Robin's florist

Grower's Responsibilities: Forwards the wholesaler's request to the Gardener and supplies the flowers
to the wholesaler from the gardener

Gardener's Responsibilities: Receives the request from the grower and plants and picks the requested flowers

Flower Arranger's Responsibilities: Receives the flowers from Robin's Florist and makes a nice bouquet
to amaze Robin and then sends the finished product to Robin's Florist ready for delivery.

Delivery Person's Responsibilities: Receives the bouquet from the Robin's florist and delivers them to Robin.

Robin: Robin opens the door to her house and is flat out astonished by the flowers and is ready to propose to Chris.

